    <abstract id="aspace_4f9c3d01b9da383ee8cd36fa90a0185f">This collection consists of material related to Shirley Kubik (1934-2023) and her career as a hostess with Trans World Airlines (TWA) from 1957-1958. Included are photographs, training manuals, performance reviews, flight diaries and notebooks, dining menus, and two TWA hostess hats.</abstract>
