  <bioghist id="aspace_55cd1a2afb3f4c33a410047643d060bb">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Shirley Kubik was born in Cicero, Illinois on September 21, 1934 to Edward and Edna (Stepka) Kubik. After graduating from high school, Kubik competed in local beauty contests, winning several. In 1957, Kubik was hired as an air hostess with Trans World Airlines (TWA). She resigned from TWA in 1958 to marry Charles Ettner. Kubik died on March 18, 2023.</p>  </bioghist>
